rows.label: tev056901_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev056901_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Ngogo about the Nopon who have come to NLA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev056901_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Ngogo if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Ngogo if the Nopon will fight.

rows.label: tev056901_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Ngogo about recent developments.

rows.label: tev056901_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Ngogo about recent developments.

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0001
rows.name: Mira get really dangerous once nasty Prone show up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0002
rows.name:
Lots of Nopon get eaten, in fact. So elder and Ngogo
come to city where friends of Tatsu can protect them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0003
rows.name:
As for other Nopon, maybe some come just out of
curiousness? City is full of many wonders, after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0004
rows.name:
Maybe others hoping to sell information about Mira to
ignorant human friends and earn quick buck.
Nopon never miss chance to make moolah![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, Ngogo will give friends info for free so long as
they agree to keep elder and Ngogo safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0010
rows.name:
Elder Nan is very important leader who oversees all
Nopon caravans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0011
rows.name: ...Or at least, Elder Nan USED to be.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0012
rows.name:
But other Nopon fall out of love with elder who
complain too much and never think things through.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0013
rows.name: Pretty soon Nopon stop listening to elder altogether.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0014
rows.name:
Now elder claims he about to give up ghost.
Such drama! But Nan still my elder.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG0015
rows.name:
Ngogo considering putting secret plan into action
to cheer elder up. BLADE friend should come help
when plan is ready.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meeeeh! Never! No way! Not happening!
Too dangerous![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1002
rows.name:
Sure, some brave Nopon think they are real bruisers,
but most just hire bodyguard to do fighting instead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1003
rows.name:
After all, Nopon with battle injury cannot sell as much,
and selling is living![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1004
rows.name:
This is why Nopon like Ngogo and elder make smart
choice and come live in city where human friends can
protect them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1009
rows.name:
Elder Nan keep threatening to teach Popote all there
is to know about leading Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1010
rows.name:
But what does Elder Nan know about LEADING
these days? Ngogo sense major impending disaster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1011
rows.name:
Maybe Ngogo needs to quietly step in and nudge
Popote in slightly more responsible direction...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG1012
rows.name:
Ngogo knows better than to let successor of elder turn
into big whiny wimp![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG2001
rows.name:
Elder Nan still likes to play field, even though old.
Lately, not even alien girls are safe from unwelcome
and creepy advances of elder![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG2002
rows.name:
Now everyone look at Ngogo like some kind of pervy
accomplice. Meh! So embarrassing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG2003
rows.name:
One would hope scathing lecture from Pisa finally made
Elder Nan see error of ways.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG2004
rows.name:
*sigh* Maybe time is right for Ngogo to quit job and
start new life in city like Pisa...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG3001
rows.name:
Did friend have any luck making traditional Nopon
royal cuisine?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG3002
rows.name:
No problem if friend want to skip ridiculously annoying
steps. It still counts in end![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev056901_MSG3003
rows.name:
Anyway, Ngogo is looking forward to what friend
comes up with. Good luck![ST:wait ]
